  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Published in 2021 by Leuven University Press, \"De stad op de berg\" has yet to attract significant citations or public discourse across major platforms. However, it shows promise through commercial linkage, being available on platforms like Amazon and Goodreads, indicating potential interest stemming from readers.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"De stad op de berg,\" released by Leuven University Press in 2021, provides a scholarly exploration of its designated fields, even though it has not yet garnered substantial citations or public engagement. The lack of measurable community discourse\u2014such as mentions on Wikipedia or Reddit\u2014suggests that its impact within broader societal discussions is still emerging. Nevertheless, its availability on commercial platforms indicates a baseline of potential interest among readers.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Despite the current absence of formal citations and community interactions, the book demonstrates a considerable level of commercial linkage, scoring 0.9 on a scale indicating its presence on well-known platforms such as Amazon and Goodreads. This commercial availability may signify a latent demand for the themes presented in the work, even if this interest has not translated into academic citations yet.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">In the context of scholarly communications, the challenges faced by \"De stad op de berg\" reflect a common trend for new publications where initial visibility and traction are often slow to develop. With no event data or impactful discussions recorded, the book remains within a niche audience, likely requiring targeted outreach or academic promotion to enhance its visibility within the discipline.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Looking forward, the potential for \"De stad op de berg\" to influence academic discourse lies in the continual evolution of its audience engagement strategies. If future readers and scholars discover and value the insights presented, the work may prove to be a significant academic contribution, despite its current status. The cultivation of a broader discourse surrounding its themes could lead to increased citations and public interaction over time.</p>",
